EN: Don't bring up old issues just because of this matter.

ZH: 我们不应该一直把旧事重提。
EN: We shouldn't keep rehashing old issues.

ZH: 别再旧事重提，我们已经解决了这个问题。
EN: Stop bringing up old issues, we have already resolved this problem.

